oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Political rally on Sparta square
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Political rally on the courthouse square. Signs on building are for J.O. Young and Quarles & Hunter.
The fire in 1912 destroyed the north side of the square.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
